Dr. Barry Harris is jazz pianist, bebop evangelist, and music teacher whose career spanned more than seven decades. He is notable for preserving, advocating for, and demonstrating the authentic bebop system of Charlie Parker and Bud Powell. In recent years, his teaching has garnered world-wide acclaim and a surge of interest due to video recordings of his workshops being made publicly available on YouTube. At the time of writing, the popular Barry Harris Videos YouTube channel has over 11 million total views.
